    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9374113082
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "わーい、海だー！　ねーねー早くみんなで遊びに\n行こうよ！　あ、見て見て！　あっちに屋台も出てる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay‚ it's the ocean! Hey‚ hey‚ let's all go play\nLet's go! Oh‚ look‚ look! There are food stalls over there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8374113082,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5202.384456100006,
          "startTime": 40.0397957643
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.9707429248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、芽衣ちゃん！　{user}さんが\nチェックイン終わるまでもう少しここで待ってよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Mei-chan! {user}-san is\nstill checking in‚ so let's wait here a little longer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7707478206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.6707429248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "まさか{user}さんも付いてくるなんてね\nてっきり私達だけで行くのかと思ってたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't expect {user}-san would come with us too.\nI totally thought it would just be us going.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3040811539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.3040762582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "私達の誕生日は口実で、単に彼が\n休みたかっただけなんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe our birthdays were just an excuse‚ and\nhe simply wanted a break‚ don't you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9040811539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.2040749866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は{user}さんも一緒に来てくれて\n嬉しいけどなー。人数多い方が楽しいもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ Mei is happy that {user}-san came too.\nIt's more fun with more people!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9374144872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "本当はさとみさんが付いてくるはずだったんですけど\n楽しみにし過ぎて前日に熱を出しちゃったらしくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ Satomi-san was supposed to come with us‚\nbut it seems she got so excited that she got a fever the day before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.4707478206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.6707380929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "可哀そうだけど、なんだかさとみらしいね\n次の機会があれば一緒に来られるといいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's too bad‚ but somehow it feels like Satomi.\nI hope she can come with us if there's another chance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3040811539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.7374047595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……次なんてないわよ。なんで毎年あなた達と\n旅行になんて行かなきゃいけないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah… There won't be a next time. Why do I have to\ngo on trips with you guys every year?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9374144872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.5707380929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言ってるけど{user}君に\n「旅行先は沖縄がいい」って言ったのは君じゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say that‚ but weren't you the one\nwho told {user}-kun \"I want the trip to be in Okinawa‚\" right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.970745786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "どーせ断ったって強制的に参加させられるんだから\n自分の希望を言うくらい構わないでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if I refused‚ I'd be forced to participate anyway.\nSo it's fine if I at least state my preference‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.770745786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7707380929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "うちの事務所が強制参加させることはないと思うわよ\n行きたくないなら欠席でも良かったんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think our agency would ever force anyone to participate.\nIf you didn't want to go‚ wouldn't it have been fine to just skip it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.070745786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.3040699003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、うるさいわね！　福利厚生を受けないと損だと\n思っただけよ！　以上！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ shut up! I just thought it would be a waste if I don't take advantage\nof the welfare benefits! That's all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.0040775935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.4040699003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "franさん……飛行機の隣の席で\n凄く楽しそうに沖縄の観光雑誌を見てたような～……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fran-san… You seemed really happy looking at\nan Okinawa tourist magazine next to me on the plane~…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5040775935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、kanaちゃんのSNSでも「浮足立ちの\nfranちゃん」って写真付きの投稿見たような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yesterday‚ on Kana-chan's SNS‚ I think I saw a post\nwith a picture titled \"Fran-chan all excited\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8040857315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.0707396188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、franにも可愛いところがあるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ fran has cute sides too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0707396188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.2374062854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor006.m4a",
